<section class="hero">
  <h1>How Much <em>Cash?</em></h1>
  <div class="hero-subtitle">How and when can dry powder get you more bitcoin?</div>
  <p class="subtitle">A tool for the all-in holder: pick a cash share, pick a moment in the record, and see how raising it there has historically ended &mdash; in coins.</p>
</section>

