  <!-- ════════ Q3 — AND WHEN TO COME BACK ════════ -->
  <section class="hc-section" id="come-back">
    <div class="hc-eyebrow">Question three</div>
    <h2 class="hc-h2">And when to come back</h2>
    <p class="hc-lead">The rule is fixed, and it is the same one <a href="/wait-or-deploy-now">Wait, or Deploy Now?</a> uses to measure waiting: <strong>the cash rebuys at the first lower entry if one arrives within two years, and at the two-year price if none does.</strong> No timing, no discretion, no optimizer. If the dip never comes, you buy back at whatever two years later costs &mdash; sometimes more than you sold for.</p>
    <p class="hc-readout hc-readout-wide" id="hcQ3">&mdash;</p>
  </section>

